{"tid":2496104,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTv其實應該改革下D劇集時間","createTime":"2021-04-19T14:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T17:26:20.000Z","uid":51200,"like":224,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"57acdea545fadbb49316d781533b7ca35932e11b","tid":2496104,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"黃金時間播日劇講劇呢啲dum波鐘浪費時段就唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n想對ViuTv 本土製作嘅劇集時段俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，ViuTv d劇集套套都係精品<br />\n而我覺得香港精品電視劇其中一個問題就係播嘅時間去得太快<br />\nKeep唔到個熱度<br />\n精品劇連續咁播其實睇得幾辛苦<br />\n唔同TBB d 公式劇，人哋係流水作業，<br />\ntarget係堆no stake in society <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用大量宣傳係公眾場所博取眼球夾高收視率<br />\n<br />\n而Viu既宣傳得罪講句好少好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劇情又相對慢熱，<br />\n如果要公眾轉台，一定係需要慢慢煲（例如喺報紙雜誌上網平台等等）<br />\n一路播，一路煲返兩三個禮拜幫d 劇make noise<br />\n可惜viu d劇集又短，煲完都播完<br />\n其實好不利廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTv 行嘅電視劇風格同TVB完全唔同<br />\n咁有冇必要真係好似TVB咁播足星期一至五呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nViuTv嘅劇集已經少，<br />\n一日淨係播一套劇集，連續播足幾個禮拜就完<br />\n<br />\n我明白ViuTv冇資源好似TVB咁一晚播三套劇<br />\n但係ViuTv 不妨試吓<br />\n兩三套劇喺同一個禮拜混合播？<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">例如 A劇星期一三五，B劇星期二四，綜藝星期六日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣可以增加ViuTv 啲藝人係同一時間嘅出鏡率，<br />\n觀眾又冇覺得咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有咩意見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最理想當然好似日本美國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期一至五，每日都播唔同劇，一個禮拜就可以播五套劇<br />\n播足起碼10幾個禮拜<br />\n呢個做法最適合都市人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期一至五連續播同一套劇真係去得太快，其實好難追<br />\n真係得閒追個熱潮都完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590cab40d451990a48cc3bf234c3147695853c58","tid":2496104,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"大家入嚟講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c325cd5ea1ab86368713847e74b177ea0cdf6d","tid":2496104,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:56:19.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"60587f9699b6ab14215272e4a71e24490e5e2112","tid":2496104,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"Anyone<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11271aca71bfadffecc643a372aecc4d3ba1c05c","tid":2496104,"uid":24457,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:00:10.000Z","msg":"係 依家一至五日日播真係好heavy無心機追 一個禮拜播一兩集得閒睇吓唔驚catch up唔到"},{"pid":"f3d5fa55778240dd8c0ec309a0b9aa0fdd643ab9","tid":2496104,"uid":16676,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"印象中開台果時咪係咁囉<br />\n<br />\n隔住日子播, 攪到唔記得miss 左<br />\n觀眾又金魚記憶, 轉頭已經唔記得劇情, 變左無追劇癮<br />\n<img src=\"/asse